features: The interior compression straps keep your clothing and other items snug, minimizing wrinkles and maximizing packing space
Durable ripstop, poly and Bi-Tech Armor Lite™ materials cover high wear areas for maximum abrasion resistance so you don’t have to worry about that careless baggage handler at the airport
An expansion zipper offers 7 more liters of capacity in order to fit even more, while still being able to carry-on
A padded tablet sleeve, offers protection and quick access to your digital life and entertainment
The main compartments are secured by lockable, self-repairing zippers and a Central Lock Point to ensure your valuables are safe and the zippers won’t fail during the middle of a trip
External lash points are ideal to secure the bag to roof of a car for a road trip, or to hang a water bottle from while you’re moving between airport terminals
Grab handles on all sides of the bag offer mobility on the go when terrain gets too rough and you need to carry
Reflective accents help keep you seen by motor vehicles if you find yourself traveling at night
Heavy-duty wheel housing and bumper protection keep you and your bag rolling down even the bumpiest of sidewalks
A vertical quick stash pocket helps keep important items within reach, its unique orientation offers easy access to your gear even when it’s in the overhead compartment
Fabric blocking hides scuffs and stains, so no matter the abuse you put your bag through, it will always look its best
Our No Matter What™ Warranty guarantees your equipment is backed by Eagle Creek, no matter what
